00:33:55,220 --> 00:33:59,690
Benar-benar. Apa yang harus kulakukan?

393
00:33:59,690 --> 00:34:02,150
Cepat letakkan di situ!

394
00:34:02,150 --> 00:34:04,490
Oh!

395
00:34:12,320 --> 00:34:14,260
Bawalah bersamamu.

396
00:34:22,180 --> 00:34:24,220
Dia sudah pergi.

397
00:34:25,830 --> 00:34:29,960
Aih, dasar berandalan tidak punya hati.

