412
00:35:57,770 --> 00:36:00,660
<i>[Laporan Resmi]</i>

413
00:36:02,380 --> 00:36:04,650
Bagus kalau begitu.

414
00:36:05,610 --> 00:36:10,840
Na Chal Nyeo sekarang tidak akan lagi...

