558
00:48:52,240 --> 00:48:54,270
Kau bahagia sekarang?

559
00:48:54,940 --> 00:48:59,040
Pertama-tama, takdirku bukanlah kesalahanmu.

560
00:48:59,040 --> 00:49:04,180
